                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-433" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD BREST</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I produce the ham. Prisoner's Defence. The boy <hi rend="italic">chucked</hi> it at me as I was standing at the window, after carrying a box for a gentleman; it hit me on my sore heel; I turned round; the man ran over, and took me.</p>
